game.engine.stage.scene.object

Class CachedNinePatchImageSceneObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.engine.stage.scene.object.SceneObject
      • game.engine.stage.scene.object.NinePatchImageSceneObject
        • game.engine.stage.scene.object.CachedNinePatchImageSceneObject

  • public class CachedNinePatchImageSceneObject
extends NinePatchImageSceneObject
    A cahced version of the NinePatchImageSceneObject. Only if the SceneObject is resized the backed NinePatchImage will be repainted.
    Meanwhile the all drawing will be done with an image cache. Results in improved speed but more memory usage.
    Author:
    Marvin Bruns
